      <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs opacity-75 max-w-xs md:max-w-md leading-tight">
        The PPG logo is a registered trademark and Colorful Communities and We protect and beautify the world are
        trademarks of PPG Industries Ohio, Inc. © 2026 PPG Industries, Inc. All Rights Reserved
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 sm:p-4 ml-auto">
